HEADWORD: Nivose
<hw>Ni`vose"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>nix</ets>. <ets>nivis</ets>, snow.]</ety> <def>The fourth month of
the French republican calendar [1792-1806]. It commenced December 21,
and ended January 19. See <er>Vend⟦eacute⟧miaire</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
